snippet.title: Creative NFT Sandbox Game Trailer | LandBox NFT Game on WAX
snippet.description:
LandBox is a creative sandbox game coming to the WAX blockchain. You can complete challenges/tasks and find your way around the land. Interaction and mini games will exist throughout the land. 

Getting bored is something in the past. With our innovative NFT game hitting the WAX blockchain you will always find something to do. Learn more at https://thelandbox.io.

We're changing the way you play NFT games.

WHITELIST PACK SALE ON 6/24/22 @ 1PM EST.
PUBLIC PACK SALE ON 6/27/22 @ 1PM EST.

Discord - https://discord.gg/g5hyfVdp59
Twitter - https://twitter.com/landboxio
Telegram - https://t.me/landboxio
